.community_title 
  GOAL MATES
  .community_box  
    - @goal_mates.each do |goal_user|
      .user_box
        .user_pic
          = image_tag goal_user.user.avatar.url(:thumb)
        .user_name 
          = goal_user.user.fullname
    .clear
  .community_title SUPPORTERS
  %p.community_txt
    You don't have any supporters yet.  They can be a great way to stay motivated and share the satisfaction of reaching a goal.
